reviewText: DVD quality is awful. I won't have paid a buck for it.

Not much of a movie, but I have to give them points for creativity.  Another one about making porn movies - suggests that organized crime may be involved.  I wonder where they got that idea?  Short, but with a bunch of excellent 1970's adult film previews, worth the price.
This film looks like a bunch of evil remains of other movies loosely connected.
